--------------------------------------------------
About Leapfrog / SAPO Messenger
--------------------------------------------------

This is the LeapFrog Jabber Client Project for SAPO.

    * http://www.sapo.pt
    * http://messenger.sapo.pt


Official project Trac web-site:
    * http://trac.softwarelivre.sapo.pt/sapo_msg_mac

Official Subversion repository:
    * svn://svn.softwarelivre.sapo.pt/sapo_msg_mac


--------------------------------------------------
Building
--------------------------------------------------

Please read the "BUILD" file that is included with this source code release
for more information on how to build the SAPO Messenger application.


